<C>__{harvey }
<P>__{(to himself)}
<D>__{i know, we don't raise our voices in this country. it's not done.}
<A>__{harvey puts the sodden napkins down onto the bar. he looks at himself in the mirror behind the bar and rubs his chest. he sighs and glances around the room. he sees kate and recognizes her.}
<C>__{harvey }
<P>__{(to kate)}
<D>__{i'm sorry.}
<A>__{kate looks up. beat.}
